A
B
C
A + B + C = 0
\sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac A{5n+1}+\frac B{5n+2}+\frac C{5n+3}
\forall n\ge1 \wedge \forall 1\leq j \leq 3
\frac{1}{5n+j}=\frac{1}{5n}-\frac{j}{5n(5n+j)}=\frac{1}{5n}+O(\frac{1}{n^2})
\forall n\ge1
\frac{A}{5n+1}+\frac{B}{5n+2}+\frac{C}{5n+3}=\frac{(A+B+C)}{5}\frac{1}{n}+O(\frac{1}{n^2})
A+B+C=0
